@page "/"

<PageTitle>Shiny BLE Sample</PageTitle>

<h1>Shiny BLE Sample</h1>

<p>This sample demonstrates Bluetooth Low Energy scanning and device interaction using the Web Bluetooth API via Shiny.BluetoothLE.Blazor.</p>

<div class="card mt-3">
    <div class="card-body">
        <h5 class="card-title">BLE Scanner</h5>
        <p class="card-text">Scan for nearby Bluetooth LE devices, connect, and interact with their services and characteristics.</p>
        <a href="blescan" class="btn btn-primary">Open Scanner</a>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="alert alert-info mt-3">
    <strong>Note:</strong> Web Bluetooth requires HTTPS and a compatible browser (Chrome, Edge, Opera). The user must grant permission for each device.
</div>
